Sentencas: In the preset study, a new identifier system has been proposed for optimal model estimation of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) stacks.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: To afford an appropriate identification system, the voltage-current profile of the system has been considered.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: The main idea is to minimize the Mean Squared Error (MSE) value between the actual output voltage of the stack and the output value achieved by the proposed model.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: Here, the MSE minimization has been established based on a new improved metaheuristic technique, called Fractional-order Social Network Search algorithm.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: The main advantage of the proposed technique is that it provides better trade-off between the global optimum and local optimum values.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: After system designing, it has been implemented to a studied case and its results are put in comparison with several latest techniques with considering two scenarios.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: One scenario with constant pressure and variable temperature and one other scenario with constant pressure and variable temperature.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm

Sentencas: Final results indicate that the presented identification system provides satisfying results against the other compared methods in optimum system identification of the SOFCs.
Titulo: System estimation of the SOFCs using fractional-order social network search algorithm
